Name: Walsh Company Opened New Office & PoE Lighting Showroom in Morristown
Post Summary:
PoE lighting
Walsh Company
General Contractor
Project Management
Aside Text:
Walsh Company, LLC is a multi-service advisory organization that specializes in client representation and project management services. Founded in 2003 by Edward S. Walsh, The Walsh Company has developed into a successful enterprise of highly accomplished professionals headquartered in Morristown.

Walsh PoE Lighting, division of Walsh Company has a PoE Lighting systems showroom. Please make an appointment to visit & let us show you more.

Name: Walsh Company Proclamation
Post Summary: Walsh Company and Walsh PoE Lighting have proudly opened their new showroom and office space in Morristown, NJ at 22 Speedwell Ave. This is the second time that Walsh Company has had its office headquartered in Morristown.
Post Body:
Walsh Company and Walsh PoE Lighting have proudly opened their new showroom and office space in Morristown, NJ at 22 Speedwell Ave. This is the second time that Walsh Company has had its office headquartered in Morristown.

Originally established in 2003 with seven employees, the company developed into a successful firm that steadily grew to 60 employees becoming a strong partner in the Morristown community. In 2012 the Walsh Company sold and remained based in Morristown till 2017.  Currently, Mr.Walsh’s vision to relaunch Walsh Company and launch Walsh PoE Lighting is now official. With 15 employees and room to grow the office proudly holds New Jersey’s first PoE lighting showroom.

As project specialists in development, project management, and construction management, Walsh Company understands the full range of challenges involved throughout the project process. Drawing on the teams extensive knowledge and expertise, they are able to execute all phases of their clients' projects from start to finish.

Some current projects include the New Jersey Hall of Fame, Kearny Shopping Center, NJ Urology, Jacobs Levy, Vincent House at Delbarton,and Newmark Knight Frank office Headquarters.

Founder and President, Edward S. Walsh, is very excited about the new venture and looks forward to continued success in Morristown.
